headline: Costco is fighting to keep its DEI program as major companies roll back initiatives
summary: Costco’s (COST) Board of Trustees is standing firm as many of the biggest companies in the U.S. scale back or scrap their diversity, equity, and inclusion (DEI) initiatives.
